I used an Arduino Mega 2560 Microcontroller Board

Because of this you must change the code in three seperate files 
to suit not only your microcontroller board but also the device you are programing on
The three files are:
1. ultrasonic.c 
2. lcd.c
3. makefile

For the first and second file the DDR and ports will not work 
if you are on a different board or different wiring.

For the makefile a multiple things will be wrong because your computer will be different
then mine and I still do not understand this file either, you may need to use an AI to figure it out

And to run the code you must type into the terminal within the folder/directory 
that these files are in "make flash" which hopefully should compile and run the code.
